<% content_for :title do %>PostcardMailer.us Help<% end %><p class="section">Hello <%= @email %>,</p><h2 class="heading">WELCOME TO POSTCARDMAILER.US!</h2><p class="section">Thank you for requesting help with PostcardMailer.us. Below you'll find instructions for using our service through email commands.</p><h2 class="heading">Available Commands</h2><%= render 'command_mailer/signup_instructions' %><%= render 'command_mailer/adduser_instructions' %><%= render 'command_mailer/postcard_instructions' %><%= render 'command_mailer/help_instructions' %><h2 class="heading">Important Notes</h2><ul class="list"><li class="list-item">New accounts require verification before you can send postcards</li><li class="list-item">Make sure addresses are complete and formatted correctly</li><li class="list-item">Image attachments should be clear and high resolution for best results</li><li class="list-item">The nickname in the email address identifies the recipient</li></ul>